 motion of low mass objects and briefly\ndiscuss how the observed displacements of star clusters and active galactic\nnuclei from the centers of their host galaxies can be used to constrain FDM.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 11 May 2021 18:00:35 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 27 Jul 2021 21:13:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-08-11"}
