se coherence of pairs of Cooper\npairs. So our study provides a promising way to realize the charge-4e\nsuperconductivity in a bilayer system.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 12 May 2021 03:07:01 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 9 Aug 2021 07:14:43 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 8 Apr 2022 07:16:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-05-16"}
