ource of power\nin Eastern and South-Eastern Europe - representing a potential risk for the\nlong term decarbonization targets within the European Union.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 12 May 2021 14:00:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-05-13"}
